syllabus_objectives:
In details, after completing the course, trainees will:
- To comprehensively understand what NDA is;
- To classify NDA types depending purpose of use;
- To find the NDA checklist; and
- To be able to use NDA checklist and apply the contents

After this course, trainees can:
• Make a professional presentation;
  • Make a good slide;
  • Be more confident in giving speech.

After this course, trainees can:
• Make a professional emails;
  • Know how to reply well in special cases: complanation, delay, ask for help, refuse,etc.

In details, after completing the course, trainees will:
- Be aware of customer contract review process in Fsoft;
- Understand some common type of customer contract
- Have basic knowledge of customer contract terms;

After the course, trainees can:
• Have the right mindset about change;
• Know the importance of management team at the company changes ;
• Identify the impacts of change to team;
• Apply the procedure of making changes into your current work;
• Practice some skill to apply changes successfully.

